{"tid":751782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"父母遺傳左病比你，有無責任幫你醫？","createTime":"2018-07-22T07:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T15:39:28.000Z","uid":152005,"like":145,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"68c4c3fcd6ec4e7a61b9620673ca5b48f21394fe","tid":751782,"uid":152005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"交代下背景，就快廿歲<br />\n爸爸：<br />\n遺傳尿酸高血壓，糖尿都就快。<br />\n阿媽：眼疾<br />\n同佢地討論後：自己嘅病應該自己醫乜野都唔關佢地事，唔好賴落佢地身上。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母又唔撚見你有錢遺傳我<br />\n一句講曬窮就咪撚生仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：父母有責任幫你醫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮：自己有手有腳唔識搵錢醫？"},{"pid":"7dd7177d38ac38226f19db631a9b3e24b43eff1a","tid":751782,"uid":152005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"有無人講下老豆老媽遺傳乜野比你地？"},{"pid":"26998950808b10b52412764e87fb5132fd695bc5","tid":751782,"uid":176063,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a6f8d08290a4d7816dc25e76b1e9754a902cd31","tid":751782,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"好健康"},{"pid":"8f9f37a4ab16a3c7f1de56989d4a601e6494930b","tid":751782,"uid":123456,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">濕疹女</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c005cf6d5f769f075f357b487fb221d67e79f308","tid":751782,"uid":152005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f9f37a4ab16a3c7f1de56989d4a601e6494930b","tid":751782,"uid":123456,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">濕疹女</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c797fc8172cb65f97b1b9866fda87888a6ec429d","tid":751782,"uid":110298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"有病就應該醫"},{"pid":"40b16ec11a10e5e29fa32e331a24a244af874bc2","tid":751782,"uid":46347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"就算係咪佢遺傳俾你佢都有責任架喎<br />\n前提係你地真係一家人 佢點對你你點對佢嗰隻"},{"pid":"581a21fbde04f5b559c1f35f495d32786f3bd9a2","tid":751782,"uid":54581,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"我父母兩系有9成人都健健康康 靚仔靚女<br />\n<br />\n其中有一啲祖先有啲毛病<br />\n<br />\n例如心臟病 腸胃潰瘍 樣柒 等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我就集百家大成 中齊晒<br />\n<br />\n咁你覺我賴唔賴上一代好？"},{"pid":"e60bedd296a7414fc20e43853573a4e4fc120640","tid":751782,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:05:00.000Z","msg":"我天生左眼近視右眼遠視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4830f7abe9426627fa1728ba2396590cdd54ffc5","tid":751782,"uid":12421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"581a21fbde04f5b559c1f35f495d32786f3bd9a2","tid":751782,"uid":54581,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"我父母兩系有9成人都健健康康 靚仔靚女<br />\n<br />\n其中有一啲祖先有啲毛病<br />\n<br />\n例如心臟病 腸胃潰瘍 樣柒 等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我就集百家大成 中齊晒<br />\n<br />\n咁你覺我賴唔賴上一代好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"你唔應該賴上一代<br />\n<br />\n但上一代有責任改善你嘅情況"},{"pid":"714d71105188ff2fd6a718b6f5a88c6465c47909","tid":751782,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:45:27.000Z","msg":"手汗症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d2016e8f7e577365f3d65f97ad823ed54cf985","tid":751782,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"得閒磨下刀"},{"pid":"998594d34942effe1c2f4d6a3dacc9f93d6988fb","tid":751782,"uid":44391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abe15e2cbf916d93297c13b09f45e807052224d0","tid":751782,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:10:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cff8b18671c352a40088e0b005088832d4702f7","tid":751782,"uid":51933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"點先知係遺傳定後天?"},{"pid":"2bfb1df72e033e1676270fc44d6e26eba243d555","tid":751782,"uid":141268,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"膠：啊當同夏娃遺傳左死亡呢件事比我地，我地應唔應該賴佢地？<br />\n<br />\n認真：個問題，我覺得你分析錯左方向<br />\n就算你個病同父母既病一d啦能都無<br />\n有責任感既父母都會帶你去醫<br />\n無責任感既父母，永遠都係會無不負責任<br />\n<br />\n但掉番轉頭，一旦你父母老喇<br />\n要你負責照顧佢地喇<br />\n你會負責任定唔負責任？<br />\n<br />\n一個人負唔負責任，唔關其他人，包括父母事。<br />\n如果負責任呢件事係遺傳既話，咁樓主肯定係一個唔負責任既人。<br />\n<br />\n真相係，你或者你父母，負唔負責任，純粹只係一個個人選擇既問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得你既父母係某d個人選擇上面有問題有唔好，又改變唔到佢地。<br />\n我認為你可以做既野，就只有提醒自己大個後，不要成為佢地呢種人。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，父母亦都有自己既問題，你亦都會大個，你要開始學識用自己方法解決問題。<br />\n唔係話你一定有方法解決問題，只係去&quot;尋找&quot;和&quot;學習&quot; 如何去解決一個問題。<br />\n而係解決到問題之前，你更加要去學習&quot;如何面對&quot;一個未解決到既問題。<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你。"},{"pid":"2f4ad66b7e4e63d88be47368e6af81978fd5a161","tid":751782,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cff8b18671c352a40088e0b005088832d4702f7","tid":751782,"uid":51933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"點先知係遺傳定後天?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"都有d好明顯係遺傳病，<br />\n而唔會自發嘅，<br />\n例如唐氏綜合症，血友病，地中海貧血。"},{"pid":"9a0e02e637c188bdd085b3dfec53751e48805196","tid":751782,"uid":156819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd7177d38ac38226f19db631a9b3e24b43eff1a","tid":751782,"uid":152005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"有無人講下老豆老媽遺傳乜野比你地？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83b3243f85eccd51d05e9d3413ca1e707f3b9fe","tid":751782,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"陰陽眼"},{"pid":"16a338e89cd3f30c445176104419157be5f67520","tid":751782,"uid":187198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"180身高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a13b15cd6922b4e74b7daaa2c61893f1688ae44","tid":751782,"uid":41432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"父母遺傳左矮同醜樣比我,有冇責任俾錢我整容?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56383f407485034a1c7bd3bfbde438a64ffde2b4","tid":751782,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a13b15cd6922b4e74b7daaa2c61893f1688ae44","tid":751782,"uid":41432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"父母遺傳左矮同醜樣比我,有冇責任俾錢我整容?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"矮無得救...."},{"pid":"cec6129f35e2c1e9cd10f3bf6cb00a40600bf589","tid":751782,"uid":41432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56383f407485034a1c7bd3bfbde438a64ffde2b4","tid":751782,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a13b15cd6922b4e74b7daaa2c61893f1688ae44","tid":751782,"uid":41432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"父母遺傳左矮同醜樣比我,有冇責任俾錢我整容?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"矮無得救...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"係,所以要從金錢方面索償返精神方面既損失"},{"pid":"3b55cd638d450f9935d93675ec581301f31c6d90","tid":751782,"